txt.en: 'It can be no coincidence the entrance to Carchost is defended by an entire encampment of Orcs. Some unpleasant surprise waits within. I have watched many comings and goings of Uruk-hai through the iron gates at the base of the tower.\n\n'I believe, were you to find your way in there, you might wreak some havoc and spoil the surprise.'
You should defeat Uruk-hai within the Towers of the Teeth.
You have defeated many Uruks within the Towers of the Teeth and confirmed that a large group of the Enemy move within the towers.
Defeat Uruks within the Towers of the Teeth ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Thurindol believes that many more foes hide and wait for the Host of the West within the Towers of the Teeth.
Defeated many Uruks within the Towers of the Teeth.
